{
  "stem": "14928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in the family's-- not her family, but the family we stayed with, their sister had a house there and a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is where she was hiding in the attic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, their whole family that I stayed with-- not in the ghetto-- were hiding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went into a basement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the basement was outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to go around from the outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My cousin's brother-in-law, it was his family and his mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were in that basement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he wanted to go and get something, maybe some food into the-- they didn't know how long they have to stay there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Germans saw him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he didn't want-- he didn't want his family to be killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he didn't even get close to the basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was walking away, the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So they killed him right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The family was saved in the basement and so was my girlfriend in the attic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the-- I was in the working ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My cousin got me out, 5 o'clock or 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't tell you exactly when.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he said, let's go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're going to stay with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in the working ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they did a lot of tricks with the working ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now they said, all the Jews that are alive in the old ghetto-- in the business ghetto should come to the working ghetto, that nothing is going to happen to them anymore.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just did what they did, and nothing's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, everybody came here to this ghetto already.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
